itemDescription: British Labour hereditary and life peer (born 1935)

wikipedia_page.main: Julian Pascoe Francis St Leger Grenfell, 3rd Baron Grenfell, Baron Grenfell of Kilvey (born 23 May 1935) is a Labour hereditary peer and former member of the House of Lords known for his strong Europhile views.
